#CHIP YM2203
#CLOCK 3579545

; YM2203 (OPN) FM + SSG Mixed Test
;
; Tests the YM2203 with FM and SSG channels playing simultaneously.
; This validates that both subsystems work without interference.
;
; FM channels (3) play melodic content
; SSG channels (3) play harmonic support and bass

#TRACK 0

TEMPO 120

; FM melody with SSG harmony
c4 & c3 . d4 & d3 . e4 & e3 .

r4

; FM polyphony with SSG bass
c4 & e4 & g4 & c3 .

r2

; SSG rhythmic accompaniment under FM lead
f4 . g4 . a4 . & c4 . c4 . c4 .

r2

; All channels in unison (brief)
c4 & c4 & c4 .

r2

#END
